<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(ابو الوفاء)</span> واعظ.<span class="c5"> من آثاره:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
